{"tid":506562,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【唔撚死都冇撚用】內地女友提分手 19歲仔石硤尾跳橋","createTime":"2017-12-22T10:35:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-23T08:46:36.000Z","uid":37661,"like":15,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e6d6d17664ebeb38d0d9c52a106bce154e9441ce","tid":506562,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T10:35:35.000Z","msg":"內地女友提分手 19歲仔石硤尾跳橋<br />\n<br />\n即時突發  2017-12-22 07:13:09 HKT<br />\n<br />\n【14：54更新】新增動新聞<br />\n<br />\n【14:46更新】青年稍後轉送瑪嘉烈醫院，現時情況危殆<br />\n<br />\n早上約7時，深水埗石硤尾邨美山樓對開行人天橋，一名姓黃19歲男子跨過圍欄墮下，頭手腳受傷倒臥10米地下，仍然清醒，途人發現報警。救護員到場將傷者送明愛醫院。<br />\n<br />\n警方調查指，事主是<span style=\"color: red;\">新移民</span>，女友在內地，疑女友提出分手，他不堪打擊跳橋自殺。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171222/57612397\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171222%2F57612397&d=dU1EKunJxGMjOSOd%2Bn8PejA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=ad222f35\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171222%2F57612397&h=634fd5bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171222/57612397</a>"},{"pid":"94194c82ca1a9c10d90b1e588435c449b09c83d2","tid":506562,"uid":12158,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T12:31:38.000Z","msg":"被女飛就死，呢種人死咗佢就啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a023eb79dc01c8ef12d5111bcb432b74282035c","tid":506562,"uid":15815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T12:53:59.000Z","msg":"蝗二代🤷🏻&zwj;♂️<br />\n食米線食懵左"},{"pid":"5bd2ec8836a54bf2c3a961b4976e9c8a0e52b4db","tid":506562,"uid":99700,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score